snippet.title: The Legend of Goose: The Honk Waker - Mod Release Showcase
snippet.description:
Download link: https://gamebanana.com/mods/543673

The Goose is Loose and ready to honk and spread chaos across Hyrule!
After 4 years, I am finally releasing a new mod. Time sure flies like a goose!

This is a mod pack that originally started as a simple Link replacement, requested by Crain from The Wind Waker Randomizer and Racing communities, back in 2022.

However, I enjoyed working on the mod so much that I expanded it into a large mod pack with a lot of changes, taking months of work to complete.

What does this mod include? Watch the video to find out!

If you would like to support me and my work, feel free to leave a like, comment and subscribe as I would like to continue growing my channel and post more videos! 

I also have a Patreon where you can help me to create more content and videos. 
Every bit of support means a lot, so thank you very much.

Twitter / X: https://twitter.com/BigSharkZ
My Discord server: https://discord.gg/z95kbaAPpU
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/BigSharkZ
Paypal: https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/BigSharkZ

Special thanks to Praecipua, Crain and Joshy / JoshuaFE8 for helping with this mod!

https://www.youtube.com/@praecipuaWW
https://twitter.com/PraecipuaWW

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgoeIyEujE_yV6nQmTyApIw
https://twitter.com/JoshuaFEH

https://x.com/CrainWWR

Enjoy! :)

#untitledgoosegame #thelegendofzeldathewindwaker #zelda
